---
slug: api/payment-methods
format: json
method: get
searchable: false
---

{% comment %} Get user_uuid {% endcomment %}
{%- if context.current_user -%}
     {%- comment -%} Logged-in user {%- endcomment -%}
     {%- assign user_uuid = context.current_user.external_id -%}
{%- else -%}
     {%- comment -%} Guest user {%- endcomment -%}
     {%- assign user_uuid = context.session.event_guest_uuid -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Never query with a blank contact_uuid — a null property filter is ignored, which would
  return every user's saved cards (including the chargeable payment_method_token).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if user_uuid == blank -%}
[]
{%- else -%}
{%- graphql cards = "modules/events/payment_method/get_payment_method", contact_uuid: user_uuid, size: 50 | dig: 'items', 'results' -%}
{{ cards }}
{%- endif -%}